p: \rI've been studying this bizarre rock formation ever since we arrived in Holon.
\rIt's definitely not natural... it can't be. Perhaps it was built as some sort of ancient effigy.
\rA lot of the researchers here think some sort of ancient kingdom, many years ago, is an indirect reason for all these Deltas.
\rI heard about a similar kingdom in Kalos- maybe there's a connection?
